title: Test Drive Unlimited (PS2) (NTSC) (Fabio5ilva)
description:
Test Drive Unlimited (PS2)

Region: NTSC

Year: 2007

A current-gen version entry in the respected Test Drive franchise, based on Eden Studios' next-gen Test Drive Unlimited. Packed with many of the world's most luxurious vehicles, more than one thousand miles of open Hawaiian roads, a challenging single player game and a host of online options, Test Drive Unlimited is M.O.O.R.: Massively Open Online Racing - the ultimate online automotive gaming experience. Test Drive Unlimited system retain most of the core gameplay features of next-gen games, including endless miles of streaming Hawaiian roads, server-based online play, over 70 luxury supercars, multiplayer and single-player modes, player-created races, car upgrades and downloadable content.
